episodes.title: These Cult Leaders' Antics Infuriate Me | Twin Flames Universe Body Language and Verbal Analysis
episodes.description:
Disclaimer: What I say in this video is merely my opinion. Nothing I reference should be used as any form of legal or professional evidence.

Part One: https://youtu.be/4aDGV8dtU8w
Original Interview: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ePUn0qbTZY&t=6s&ab_channel=OfficialW5

Twin Flames University leaders recently did an interview with Canada's W5 (linked above) after a number of documentaries exposing their practices came out and caused the two to face substantial public backlash. People have requested that I analyze the nonverbal communication during the interview and compare it to the footage of them during their various teaching sessions or church meetings. This is part two of the 2-part analysis. The first half is linked above or at the end of this video.
